    billing + beta — manual unlock now; gateway later:
    + Phase A — Subscription truth
        + A1 subscriberStatus helpers (active plan, status, period end, cap interpretation) DONE
        + A2 load subscriber_entitlements with session / pass into app DONE
        + A3 owner shell rule: active subscriber (+ optional owns org), not signup-time admin DONE
